Service log information
: the operational record generated when you use the Service, including fault log, software operational data (in case of failure, users can also voluntarily submit log files to the administrating server)
We use this information to:
ensure the security of the service, solve and locate problems, help us better understand how our application is running, optimize our services and improve the quality of the Service; and
to determine whether an account has been hacked or whether any improper or illegal act exists.
It is in our legitimate interests to use this information to protect the integrity of the Service and improve its operation.
Security-related information
: device operation system settings, device information including equipment brand, available space on device, Device ID, model, CPU structure, CPU model, kernel version, resolution
We use this information:
To provide a fair environment;
To solve crashes and optimize compatibility.
It is in our legitimate interests to use this information to protect the integrity of the Service and improve its operation.
