Information provided by the Company User
: your name, photo, gender (optional), mobile number (optional), email address (optional) and other personal information (job title (optional), department (optional), chat messages, file folder, files, saved collections, to-do list, address book (enterprise), approval records (if you use this function) and email configuration information)
